                Worth every cent — I have no words!"
            </p>
            <div class="testi-author">
                <div class="testi-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--rose))">SK</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="testi-name">Sipho &amp; Kezia</div>
                    <div class="testi-event">Wedding · June 2024</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testi-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="testi-stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="testi-text">
                "My daughter's 18th birthday was magical! The balloon arch and
                table styling were so gorgeous. Everyone was asking who did the
                decor. So professional and so talented!"
            </p>
            <div class="testi-author">
                <div class="testi-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal),var(--violet))">NP</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="testi-name">Nomvula P.</div>
                    <div class="testi-event">18th Birthday · August 2024</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>


<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     CTA BANNER
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="cta-banner-content reveal">
        <p class="cta-eyebrow">✦ Ready to create something beautiful?</p>
        <h2 class="cta-title">
            Let's Make Your<br>
            <em>Dream Event</em> a Reality
        </h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">
            Contact us today for a free consultation. We'd love to hear about your
            vision and help you bring it to life — beautifully.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@bloomandco.co.za" class="btn-white">
            ✉ Get in Touch Today
        </a>
    </div>
</section>


@section Scripts {
    <script>
        /* ── Smooth anchor scrolling ── */
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
                if (target) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
                }
            });
        });

        /* ══════════════════════════════════════════
           SERVICE GALLERY DATA
           Replace emoji placeholders with real <img> src paths later
        ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
        const serviceData = {
            baby: {
                icon: '🍼',
                title: 'Baby Shower Gallery',
                desc: 'A collection of our favourite baby shower setups — soft, dreamy and utterly beautiful.',
                items: [
                    { emoji: '🌸', label: 'Flower Wall', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#F4A7B5,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '🎀', label: 'Balloon Arch', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#FADADD,#F4A7B5)' },
                    { emoji: '🍼', label: 'Table Setup', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '🌷', label: 'Centrepiece', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#F4A7B5,#9B72CF)' },
                    { emoji: '✨', label: 'Backdrop', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '💕', label: 'Full Setup', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#F4A7B5)' },
                ]
            },
            bridal: {
                icon: '👰',
                title: 'Bridal Shower Gallery',
                desc: 'Elegant, luxurious spaces designed to make every bride-to-be feel like royalty.',
                items: [
                    { emoji: '💍', label: 'Ring Table', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#F0D080)' },
                    { emoji: '🌹', label: 'Floral Setup', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '🥂', label: 'Champagne Bar', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#F0D080,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '👑', label: 'Throne Chair', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '🕯️', label: 'Candle Decor', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#9B72CF)' },
                    { emoji: '💐', label: 'Bouquet Display', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#F4A7B5)' },
                ]
            },
            birthday: {
                icon: '🎂',
                title: 'Birthday Party Gallery',
                desc: 'Bold, joyful setups for every age — from adorable first birthdays to milestone celebrations.',
                items: [
                    { emoji: '🎂', label: 'Cake Table', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#2ABFBF,#9B72CF)' },
                    { emoji: '🎈', label: 'Balloon Arch', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#2ABFBF)' },
                    { emoji: '🎉', label: 'Party Setup', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#2ABFBF)' },
                    { emoji: '🌟', label: 'Star Theme', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '🎊', label: 'Entrance', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#2ABFBF,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '🎁', label: 'Gift Table', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#9B72CF)' },
                ]
            },
            wedding: {
                icon: '💍',
                title: 'Wedding Gallery',
                desc: 'Breathtaking ceremony and reception setups that turn your love story into art.',
                items: [
                    { emoji: '💒', label: 'Ceremony Arch', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#F4A7B5)' },
                    { emoji: '🌿', label: 'Aisle Decor', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#2ABFBF,#9B72CF)' },
                    { emoji: '🕯️', label: 'Table Styling', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '💐', label: 'Floral Wall', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#F4A7B5,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '🍾', label: 'Reception', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#2ABFBF)' },
                    { emoji: '💫', label: 'Entrance Setup', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#2ABFBF)' },
                ]
            },
            balloon: {
                icon: '🎈',
                title: 'Balloon Artistry Gallery',
                desc: 'Stunning balloon installations that add the ultimate WOW factor to any space.',
                items: [
                    { emoji: '🎈', label: 'Organic Garland', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#F4A7B5)' },
                    { emoji: '🌈', label: 'Rainbow Arch', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#2ABFBF,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '🔢', label: 'Number Balloons', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '💜', label: 'Balloon Wall', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#2ABFBF)' },
                    { emoji: '🌸', label: 'Floral Balloon', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#F4A7B5,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '✨', label: 'Grand Arch', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#9B72CF)' },
                ]
            },
            table: {
                icon: '🕯️',
                title: 'Table Setup Gallery',
                desc: 'Every table is a canvas — elegant styling from charger plates to bespoke centrepieces.',
                items: [
                    { emoji: '🕯️', label: 'Candle Setting', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#E8607A)' },
                    { emoji: '🌹', label: 'Floral Centre', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#E8607A,#F4A7B5)' },
                    { emoji: '🍽️', label: 'Full Place Set', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '🥂', label: 'Glass Styling', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#2ABFBF,#D4A843)' },
                    { emoji: '📋', label: 'Menu Cards', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#F4A7B5,#9B72CF)' },
                    { emoji: '💎', label: 'Luxury Setting', bg: 'linear-gradient(135deg,#9B72CF,#2ABFBF)' },
                ]
            }
        };

        /* ══════════════════════════════════════════
           GALLERY OPEN / CLOSE
        ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
        const grid = document.getElementById('servicesGrid');
        const panel = document.getElementById('galleryPanel');
        const backBtn = document.getElementById('galleryBackBtn');
        const galleryGrid = document.getElementById('galleryGrid');
        const panelIcon = document.getElementById('galleryPanelIcon');
        const panelTitle = document.getElementById('galleryPanelTitle');
        const panelDesc = document.getElementById('galleryPanelDesc');

        function openGallery(serviceKey) {
            const data = serviceData[serviceKey];
            if (!data) return;

            // Populate panel
            panelIcon.textContent = data.icon;
            panelTitle.textContent = data.title;
            panelDesc.textContent = data.desc;

            galleryGrid.innerHTML = '';
            data.items.forEach((item, i) => {
                const el = document.createElement('div');
                el.className = 'gallery-item';
                el.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="gallery-item-inner" style="background:${item.bg}">
                        <span>${item.emoji}</span>
                        <span class="gallery-item-label">${item.label}</span>
                    </div>`;
                galleryGrid.appendChild(el);

                // Staggered entrance animation
                setTimeout(() => el.classList.add('visible'), 80 + i * 70);
            });

            // Slide
            grid.classList.add('is-hidden');
            panel.classList.add('is-open');

            // Scroll to services section top
            document.getElementById('services').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
        }

        function closeGallery() {
            panel.classList.remove('is-open');
            grid.classList.remove('is-hidden');

            // Remove visible class from items (reset for next open)
            galleryGrid.querySelectorAll('.gallery-item').forEach(el => el.classList.remove('visible'));
        }

        // Attach click to each service card
        document.querySelectorAll('.service-card[data-service]').forEach(card => {
            card.addEventListener('click', () => openGallery(card.dataset.service));
        });

        // Back button
        backBtn.addEventListener('click', closeGallery);
    </script>
}
